Within the licensed scope, Licensee may make ordinary technical copies and
perform ordinary build, bundling, transpilation, minification, tree-shaking,
caching, hosting, deployment, backup, and disaster-recovery steps necessary to
exercise the rights above, provided those steps do not expose Espalier as a
standalone asset, create Source Code rights, remove required notices, or exceed
the Order Form scope.

Unless the Order Form states otherwise, Production Use is limited to Licensee's
internal business applications and Licensee-branded products. Any OEM,
reseller, private-label, marketplace, template, app-builder, or developer-tool
use requires a separate written agreement.

